{"tid":724251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"笑啦大家可以盡情笑啦","createTime":"2018-06-30T20:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T21:36:40.000Z","uid":82698,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2377436bcfca9f11b59ab2e277ebffb25522886","tid":724251,"uid":82698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T20:09:23.000Z","msg":"反朗反美斯迷可以盡情笑啦 如你地所願一齊登機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗下兩個都應該係最後一屆世界盃 再有下屆都唔會以呢個強度出現<br />\n真係欣賞足球既 諗下美斯做既野有幾不可思議 <br />\n諗下牙朗有幾努力意志力有幾強<br />\n由小學畢業鬥到出黎做野 4屆世界盃 巔足咁耐 再無機會睇佢地係世界最大舞台踢波<br />\n以後睇阿根廷唔會再見到美斯 葡萄牙踢世界盃唔會再見到牙朗<br />\n互相恥笑之間 見証住一個時代既落幕 <br />\n兩個番到球會應該仲有幾年鬥下 下個世界盃？無啦"},{"pid":"77812c7a2c65a7ac5334f92db6987f6f49d38cb3","tid":724251,"uid":135960,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T20:10:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb6a46ab56081e34abf840139069663a9b252660","tid":724251,"uid":135960,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T20:10:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39d859f27e094e00466a6ac9f68388c55c9db826","tid":724251,"uid":82698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T21:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔笑啦 留返拜戈先笑算 梳</blockquote>拜山</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好風趣阿你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ed50327e8aaa9f6d3b1412fb2a5608e9daec10","tid":724251,"uid":107671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T21:10:29.000Z","msg":"係呀盡情笑，佢地應該笑得開心過你，袋住唔知幾多億等退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cdafdc8d5bc7fc1ce618fa0e3722f913f5c644","tid":724251,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T21:16:34.000Z","msg":"反曬兩個 笑到仆街"},{"pid":"ecddaef379809d571cdcd04227a4ce3d37b9fb6a","tid":724251,"uid":4990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T21:18:29.000Z","msg":"唔笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"